Quyen Tran is with Bi c Ton and 15 others.
19 March at 17:07

Challenge #Keep_On_Running

Cc Bn Runner thn mn

Tnh hnh dch bnh nh ang ngi trn ng la, cc a im tp luyn quen thuc th hn ch t tp ng, ln u tin trong lch s Hoa L Off sn khng phi v l do Event :v

Qu nhiu l do c v hp l chng ta l l tp luyn phi khng no?

Chnh v vy Hoa L Team t chc Challenge: Keep On Running nhm to ra sn chi gip Runners tip tc gi vng tinh thn tp luyn, khuyn khch dy sm tp luyn nng cao sc khng, mi mt Runner hy l mt khng th mnh m trong x hi cng nhau vt qua i Dch Coivd-19 ny nh

Phn thng:
30 Set qu gm: 2 khu trang + 2 ly Momo + 1 gi cafe ht cao cp thng hiu Early Morning cho ngi hon thnh challenge.
5 o thun c bit cho ngi c km nhiu nht
Phn qu bc thm cho runner ti bui tng kt

Thi gian: 19/03 n 04/04
Ni dung challenge:
t nht 6 bui chy ti thiu l 5km.
4 bui chy sng c tracklog t 5h30 6h30.
BTC s chn ra 30 bn Runner c s bui chy nhiu nht theo th t t trn xung.

Cch thc tham gia:
Cc bn tham gia Challenge vui lng Comment ng k di STT ny :
Ti S Tham Gia Cng +
Tag thm 3 ngi bn ng Run ku gi, thch thc cng nh gip tinh thn challenge c lan ta mnh m trong cng ng nh

Challenge dnh cho tt c cc bn Runners. ng k tham gia khng gii hn thi gian, min hon thnh yu cu challenge.
Trong thi gian din ra Challenge, cc bn comment tracklog kt qu chy vo phn Reply ng k ca mnh c ghi nhn kt qu.
@ Cc bn ng k tham gia vui lng Join Stravaclub di y BTC tin ghi nhn kt qu.
https://www.strava.com/clubs/vrf-challenge
Trn trng cm n cc nh ti tr: Tiendat Dinh , Son Pham L Bo Qunh Lin v thng hiu o Thun Thng ip lun ng hnh cng cng ng runners
P/s: Gu dy sm chy sng gn 1 tun nay lm gng roy nh c nh Ai mun chy cng Gu hy ib nh!

Happy Running
